  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 2nd level of this Class Mod, if you have no more than 5 Seal Bleed and are in a scenario or fight where you have found common ground with your Sealed Beast, you can choose to take this feature. You have shown your Sealed Beast that you can be reasonable and are more than willing to use its power, but only if you are both on the same page. When you gain this feature, you advance to the third level of the Sealed Beast Class mod.</p><p>When you are under the effects of Desperate Rage, you no longer gain additional Actions to enter a Vermilion Cloak. However, you can now cast any Jutsu, as long as their sole purpose is to attempt to deal damage or kill, or to directly increase your chances of dealing damage or killing. These Jutsu don't use your Vermilion Attack Bonus and Vermilion Save DC.</p><p>Once per Long Rest, if you are reduced to less than half health, you can trigger Desperate Times as your companion briefly considers the worth of your life.</p><p>Additionally, you can use Persuasion in place of Ninshou for checks to reduce Seal Bleed.</p>",
